HEADWORD: Gluttonous
<hw>Glut"ton*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Given to
gluttony; eating to excess; indulging the appetite; voracious; <as>as, a
<ex>gluttonous</ex> age</as>.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Glut"ton*ous*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Glut"ton*ous*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gluttony</ent>⟦br⟧
